                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1932" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MGEC-0029</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10158 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">种粮大户的烦恼</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The troubles of large grain</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">罗国亮，张晓春，龙成凤，姚佳琦</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华北电力大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">南昌勇华农业开发有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">农林牧副渔业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">小型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">10 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">土地流转；种粮大户；水利设施；土地分散；规模经济；2015百优案例</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">land transfer; large grain; water conservancy facilities; land fragmentation; economies of scale</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">江西省安义县种粮大户凌继河，在外创业成功后，回家又当起了农民，承包稻田1.8万亩，还聘请100多名农民帮他管理，2013年初一次性为农民们发放年终奖140多万元，轰动一方。然而，2014年春耕在即，他却遇到了不少烦恼。耕地水利设施落后成为江西的种粮大户们所面临的最大难题，而国家在这方面的资金投入尚存在资金缺口，地方政府相关部门的工作落实并不到位。凌继河面对资金的缺口，试图申请当地银行的贷款，银行却对年销售额超200万元的粮食抵押无心理睬。凌继河只好把房产、农业机械作为抵押，获得的贷款不到10万元。随着经营面积的扩大，凌继河遭遇的压力和烦恼随之增加。土地流转价格的不确定、土地流转中的耕地分散、耕地面积的误差，这些因素都不同程度地增加了凌继河的经营成本和经营风险。另外，农资产品如种子、农药和农机价格都在上涨，这给凌继河这些种粮大户带来不小压力。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Luo Xin gu,who was used to be a large farmer-household in Anyi county of Jiangxi province, became a farmer again after success of years of pioneering work outside. With contracting 1.8 acres of paddy fields, and employ more than 100 farmers to help him manage, he payed more than 140 million year-end awards to farmers one-time early in 2013,which has created a sensation.However,as the spring ploughing of 2014 is just around the corner, he has met a lot of trouble. The biggest problem facing the large grain of Jiangxi is the poor water conservancy facilities, but there are still a funding gap of the state funds invested in this area, and the work that belongs to the related departments of the local government is not in place. Facing with the capital gap,Luo Xingu tried to apply for bank loans to local banks, but the banks paid no heed to the grain mortgage, which annual sales are over two million. Then he had to use the real estate, agricultural machinery as collateral to loans of less than 100,000 yuan.With the extension of land scale, Luo Xingu faces up with increased pressure and annoyance.Factors,such as the uncertainty prices of land transfer ,scattered cultivated land ,error between contract area and actual arable land, and so on add to operating costs and operational risks. In addition, agricultural products such as seeds, pesticides and agricultural prices are rising, which gives Luo Xingu, the large grain a big pressure.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《管理经济学》、《农业经济管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模经济理论；规模经济、规模报酬与适度规模经营；土地流转</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2015-07</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">查看全文:</th>
